<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-85-0181 </DOCNO><TEXT>The aim of a modern laboratory for analysis in reprocessing is to usehigh sensitivity methods (to limit sample masses, to simplify radiationprotection equipment and to decrease effluent production), specific techniques(for accuracy) and automation. Orientation of developments satisfyingto these criteria are presented. Some examples are given.</TEXT></DOC>